# ============================================================================
# Deployment Instructions
# ============================================================================
#
# 1. Copy this file to your server:
#    sudo nano /etc/nginx/sites-available/uamas-backend
#
# 2. Edit the file:
#    - Replace 'your-domain.com' with your actual domain or IP
#    - Replace 'YOUR_FRONTEND_DOMAIN' with your frontend URL (e.g., https://intelli-mark-swart.vercel.app)
#    - Choose either OPTION 1 (HTTP) or OPTION 2 (HTTPS) - comment out the unused option
#
# 3. Create symlink:
#    sudo ln -s /etc/nginx/sites-available/uamas-backend /etc/nginx/sites-enabled/
#
# 4. Test configuration:
#    sudo nginx -t
#
# 5. Reload nginx:
#    sudo systemctl reload nginx
#
# For HTTPS setup:
# 1. Install certbot:
#    sudo apt update
#    sudo apt install certbot python3-certbot-nginx
#
# 2. Get SSL certificate (nginx should be running with HTTP config first):
#    sudo certbot --nginx -d your-domain.com
#
# 3. Certbot will automatically modify your nginx config for HTTPS
#    Or manually uncomment OPTION 2 and comment out OPTION 1
#
# Environment Variables for Cookie Configuration:
# - HTTP deployment:  JWT_COOKIE_SECURE=False, JWT_COOKIE_SAMESITE=Lax
# - HTTPS deployment: JWT_COOKIE_SECURE=True, JWT_COOKIE_SAMESITE=None
#
# See COOKIE_FIX_GUIDE.md for troubleshooting.

